<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:nāgarī maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>vīraśrī gajapati gauḍesvara navakoṭi karnāṭa kalavaragesvara śrīpurusottamadeva māhārājāṅkara subharāije samasta
<lb n="2"/>2 Aṅka śrāhi mīna su 15 ravivāre vāre <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī jaganāthaṅkara Āijñāe <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śāmū mūraliṅkara pouku kamūmūrali māhāpā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tre bh<unclear>ā</unclear>i gokṣīre hanumantadevatā pratiṣṭhākari narasiṅghanāthadevaṅka sasaṭa 50 dhile [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Ethakū kalantarakū hanuma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>devaṅka bhogakū dī 1 ṭa [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] pulipiṭā po 2 ṭa do 1 ṭa [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] dalama cāula so 7 [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] viri solā 1 [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] ghīu so <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] gūḍa pa 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] nūṇa mī
<lb n="5" break="no"/>raśī 7 [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Etakakū sajjāre dū 1 ṭire Āpo 1 ṭa [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] cāulla A 2 ṭa dū <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] gāe 2 ṭa dū 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ma dheva [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Ee devatā pūjākari <unclear>vāhāmai</unclear> [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] kūure
<lb n="6"/>Āpo 1 ṭa [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] dū <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> pūli samalaradū <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Ebhoga Āṇamāsū Ārakū puli samalara dū <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pāe dū 1 jāi nīramāila vikārū <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> lekhā
<lb n="7"/>E bhaṇḍāraṅka Āe karivā [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] svadattāḥ paradattāṁ vā nā sahanti haranti v<unclear>ā</unclear> saṣṭirvarsasahasrāṇi viṣṭhīyāṁ mahate kri
<lb n="8" break="no"/>miḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="9"/>dakhiṇī [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
</p>

